#: ../../language/error_codes/E4209.md:1
msgid "E4209"
msgstr "E4209"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4209.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `duplicate_regex_match_binding`."
msgstr "编译器诊断名称：`duplicate_regex_match_binding`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4209.md:5
msgid "Duplicate regex match binding."
msgstr "重复的正则匹配绑定。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4209.md:7
msgid ""
"Each special binding in a regex match expression can be specified at most"
" once. Using `before` or `after` multiple times would give the same part "
"of the match more than one name."
msgstr ""
"正则匹配表达式中的每个特殊绑定最多只能指定一次。多次使用 `before` 或 `after` "
"会给匹配的同一部分赋予多个名称。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4209.md:11
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4209.md:13
msgid ""
"fn match_text(s : String) -> Unit {\n"
"  ignore(s =~ (re\"a\", before=head, before=prefix))\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4209.md:17
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4209.md:19
msgid "Use each binding label only once."
msgstr "每个绑定标签只能使用一次。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4209.md:21
msgid ""
"fn match_text(s : String) -> Unit {\n"
"  ignore(s =~ (re\"a\", before=head, after=tail))\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
